92/10/19 - v1.36

    New Features:

    * Keyboard shortcuts for many Gadgets:

      ex:  Press B  -> build.
           Press d  -> Activate autodoc path stringgadget.
           tryck D  -> Filerequester for autodoc path.
           etc.

    Bug fig:

    * Mungwall/Enforcer hit during 'hotkey lookup'

    * Chelp sometimes tried to open includefiles with bad names. Optimizebug


